content:
Bring more of your service data into Service Cloud with Service Data Kit version 4.0. This updated version includes a new Digital Engagement data bundle and new data mappings for the Knowledge and Field Service bundles, which provide easy installation of knowledge, field service, and digital engagement assets. These data assets power Service Intelligence, a data-driven solution that shows key contact center performance metrics. You can also use the Service data kit outside of Service Intelligence to ingest service-related data to Data Cloud and build your own applications.

Where: This change applies to Service Cloud in Lightning Experience in Enterprise and Unlimited editions for an additional cost.

How: If you have the Service data kit installed, upgrade or reinstall it to ensure that itâ€™s up to date. You can retrieve data assets for knowledge, field service, and digital engagement only when those features are turned on. Upgrading the data kit is necessary to access the latest enhancements to Service data model objects (DMOs).
title: Service Cloud Upgrade with Additional Assets
